org.hak5.ducky

Class CommandList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hak5.ducky.CommandList

  • public class CommandList
extends java.lang.Object
    Command table holding an entry for every valid command. The CommandList is searched through by the interpreter for a match. Implemented as a singleton object since the interpreter should never use more than one list. Therefore, the new operator will throw an exception. The newInstance method should be used instead.
    Author:
    Kevin Polulak
